<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
        <title></title>
        <style>
          @media (max-width: 768px) {
            #emailContainer {
              max-width: 480px !important;;
            }
          }

          @media (max-width: 500px) {
            #emailContainer {
              max-width: 320px !important;;
            }
          }

          /*---------------------*/
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <table style="background-color: #E9EAED; padding: 50px 0 50px 0" cellpadding="20" cellspacing="0" height="100%" width="100%" id="bodyTable">
            <tr>
                <td align="center" valign="top">
                    <table style="border: 1px solid #dfe0e4; background-color: #ffffff;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" id="emailContainer">
                        <tr>
                            <td align="left" valign="top">
                                
                                <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5; font-size: 20px;" border-collapse="collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="20" width="100%" id="emailHeader">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td align="left" valign="top">
                                             Your AviaTrading subscription has been suspended
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>

                                <table border-collapse="collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="20" width="100%" id="emailContent">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="font-size: 14px;" align="left" valign="top">

                                            <b>Although your AviaTrading subscription has been suspended, it's easy to re-activate it.</b>

                                            <br><br>

                                            It's easy to re-activate your subscription if you missed 7-day billing setup period. Login to your account and navigate to subscription page, where you can choose a plan that's right for you. Also provide required information to setup billing.
                                            <br><br>

                                            Need extra help? Our support team has the answers you need to get up and running fast. <a href="https://aviatrading.com/contacts/new">Contact us</a>
                                            <br><br><br>
                                            Sincerely, <br><b>AviaTrading Team</b>

                                            </br></br>
                                            <%= @customer_email %>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>


